metadata.name: AI PORTRAIT OF CYBADRONICA
metadata.description: Cybadronica was a mistress of the dark quantum arts in 2092. She was one of the first hybrid androids to full immerse herself in the Cybaroque quantum computer program which allowed participants to fully experience Baroque life to the full from the comfort of her tech pod. A few glitches here and there, but she spent most days in full Baroque attire, even managing to hid her headset under a large AI cyber hat. She is seen here posing for her virtual portrait by the most advanced painter robot of his day - Master AI Hendruck, who was part computer, part android and part consensus algorithm.
